<h2>👋 Welcome to ParañaqueConnect!</h2>

<p>Hello <strong><%= @resident.email %></strong>,</p>

<p>Thank you for registering with <strong>ParañaqueConnect</strong>, Parañaque City's official community reporting system!</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1e40af;">📧 Email Confirmation Required</h3>
  <p>To complete your registration and start reporting community issues, please confirm your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
</div>

<div style="text-align: center;">
  <%= link_to '✅ Confirm My Account', confirmation_url(@resident, confirmation_token: @confirmation_token), class: 'button' %>
</div>

<div class="info-box">
  <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1e40af;">Your Account Details</h3>
  <p><strong>📧 Email:</strong> <%= @resident.email %></p>
  <p><strong>👤 Role:</strong> Community Resident</p>
  <p><strong>📅 Account Created:</strong> <%= @resident.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></p>
</div>

<h3>🚀 What You Can Do (After Confirmation):</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>📝 Report Issues:</strong> Submit reports about problems in your community</li>
  <li><strong>📷 Add Photos:</strong> Upload photos to help describe the issue</li>
  <li><strong>📍 Pin Location:</strong> Use our map to pinpoint exact locations</li>
  <li><strong>💬 Add Comments:</strong> Communicate with barangay officials</li>
  <li><strong>📊 Track Progress:</strong> Monitor the status of your reports</li>
</ul>

<h3>📋 How to Report an Issue:</h3>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Click "New Report"</strong> on the dashboard</li>
  <li><strong>Choose Category:</strong> Select the type of issue (flooding, road damage, etc.)</li>
  <li><strong>Select Barangay:</strong> Choose your barangay</li>
  <li><strong>Add Details:</strong> Describe the issue and upload photos</li>
  <li><strong>Pin Location:</strong> Use the map to show exact location</li>
  <li><strong>Submit:</strong> Your report will be sent to barangay officials</li>
</ol>

